{"tid":1249494,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)洛奇與生力啤 強國與洛奇 午夜人肉列車","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T20:33:57.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9488c10fda970430bfb0e2131fc1ef5baf51bd1c","tid":1249494,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=136768a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=85582530\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=e8633ead\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1f/Escapeplan01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1f%2FEscapeplan01.jpg&h=e2ecc8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/0e/Escape_Plan_The_Extractors_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F0e%2FEscape_Plan_The_Extractors_Poster.jpg&h=3b01bbde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/33/Midnight_meat_train_ver2.jpg/220px-Midnight_meat_train_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F3%2F33%2FMidnight_meat_train_ver2.jpg%2F220px-Midnight_meat_train_ver2.jpg&h=41a1c7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.雷&middot;布雷斯林（席維斯&middot;史特龍 飾）是一名技術高超的監獄設計系統安保專家，他以越獄為生，協助測試監獄的防控態度，以免犯人逃出監獄，曾在8年內從14座防衛嚴密的重刑監獄逃脫成功，並有這方面的著作出版。一次成功越獄之後，一位中情局的美女特工潔西卡（凱特瑞納&middot;巴爾夫飾）給他帶來一份新合約，讓他挑戰一個無法以合法身份存在且滴水不漏的恐怖監獄。由於有高達500萬美圓的酬勞<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述一位香港科技大亨的女兒在一場交易中突然失蹤。當雷&middot;布瑞林及其團隊在深入追查中，發現罪魁禍首是他們以前的敵人之一的瘋狂兒子，且對方還綁走了布瑞林的愛人並將其關在名為「惡魔車站」的大型監獄中，這使布瑞林一行人準備潛入監獄中展開救援行動<br />\n<br />\n3.劇情是說里昂［Leon Kauffman］是一名藝術系夜校生，白天以攝影師為業，到處拍攝各式各樣的照片糊口，在友人的建議下，里昂開始在夜車裡半偷窺似的拍攝晚歸的夜車人群，在每個月台與車廂之間穿梭，卻也意外目睹一宗殘忍的兇殺案。深受刺激的他，企圖追縱連續殺人魔地鐵屠夫的下落，卻發現事實沒有想像中簡單，跑去報警卻被警察認為是偷拍狂，而且也讓殺人魔將目標轉向了自己&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=f6b625a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=408f5f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491ada4552d8aa393b392d9bedd36121e9f2af16","tid":1249494,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c7aca82a5e9243e31ac0831c5eaf0a66dbe915","tid":1249494,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35bb952e9bfcc05a768ac9e27f26b13bdacdc05","tid":1249494,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff774960226c3ef0ea72b1c81db2588785f276f","tid":1249494,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}